data.description: If a great location is what your looking for, this is it!  This home sits at the end of a dead end street in the desirable Washington Park subdivision, yet it's only minutes from all that Muscle Shoals has to offer!  Privacy fenced back yard with a large patio for entertaining.  With almost 2,000 sq ft on the inside, you have plenty of room to spread out.  There is also a large rec room/bonus room that could be used as a 4th bedroom if needed.  Call today to set up a showing!
